{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/1.YouMustGamble.EN.png?t=1702843032\" /><br>With each step, you'll face choices that can lead to untold riches or dire consequences. Will you risk it all to rise above?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/Summon-Combat.gif?t=1702843032\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/2.CaptureYourFoes.EN.png?t=1702843032\" /><br>Turn the odds in your favor by capturing defeated enemies and adding them to your deck. Harness their unique abilities and unleash havoc upon your foes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/Capture.gif?t=1702843032\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/3.ForgeUniqueSynergies.EN.png?t=1702843032\" /><br>As you select both a character and a loyal pet for your expedition, the choices you make extend beyond mere aesthetics. Align yourself with a single clan out of three and double down on a single clan\u2019s strengths, or pair two distinct clans for an edge in different types of encounters.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/Forge-Synergies.gif?t=1702843032\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/4.PeculiarCharacters.EN.png?t=1702843032\" /><br>Meet a cast of eccentric characters lurking within the tower's shadows. From enigmatic elves to mischievous robots, every encounter adds a touch of unpredictability to your journey.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/Characters.gif?t=1702843032\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/6.DeepMetaProgression.EN.png?t=1702843032\" /><br>Ascend the tower, not just physically, but also in power. Unlock new orbs, uncover artifacts, and enhance your characters with a robust skill tree system to shape your personal playstyle and conquer the tower's mysteries.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/Lootbox.gif?t=1702843032\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/5.ProceduralSurprises.EN.png?t=1702843032\" /><br>With each ascent, the tower reshapes its halls and challenges. Adapt and strategize as you climb higher, facing new challenges at every floor.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577460/extras/7.KeyFeatures.EN.png?t=1702843032\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>150+ Unique Orbs:</strong> Amass a collection of orbs, featuring both clan-exclusive and neutral choices.<br></li><li> <strong>Varied Partners:</strong> Randomized characters and pets, each with distinct traits, stats, and visuals.<br></li><li> <strong>Three Clans:</strong> Choose among three clans, and fuse primary and secondary clans to create varied character builds.<br></li><li> <strong>Empower Your Orbs:</strong> Choose from 20 enhancements to fortify your orbs, refining your gameplay approach.<br></li><li> <strong>Fight 30 Distinct Foes:</strong> Confront a roster of 30 distinct enemy types, each with unique behaviors and challenges.<br></li><li> <strong>Adapt with Enemy Resources:</strong> Seize enemies, their tools, and weapons to bolster your deck's strength and versatility.<br></li><li> <strong>Diverse Artifact Collection:</strong> Stumble upon 30 distinct artifacts, bestowing either empowering enhancements or daunting curses.<br></li><li> <strong>Dynamic Encounters:</strong> Experience random events, interact with shopkeepers, and engage in interactions between battles.</li></ul><br>Are you ready to challenge the shadowy depths of Gamble Tower, where every step can be decided by the roll of a dice? The ultimate gambit awaits \u2013 for only the boldest gamblers will emerge victorious.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Dafter Punks","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/ec73086e41f7821673c50380ee5acc74f6a36797.jpg"},{"name":"Forgotten Gold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/4216254baa3f0fd520aea3731557c29651f72d72.jpg"},{"name":"Evil Spirit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/296987051e95252666a83ff9f790fbdf186b9b07.jpg"},{"name":"Rich","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/0ec5368d501a258d596ea7ca2511ad4d37753ea0.jpg"},{"name":"Richer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/a09021821961a241ed2143cbd6009b7566f72b51.jpg"},{"name":"SO RICH!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/4f5cbd472f913325305f520aa661a36cc9db5247.jpg"},{"name":"Gimme that Tower!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/b2ed69f893fabeab376b8c1395d8a1f700b2ef7d.jpg"},{"name":"Gacha Whale","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/8a1839ce4f09c310e9b610263ab8ee4541fcd592.jpg"},{"name":"Newbie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/269398d6e73b0ed6ea9115503f148bcea9b9c505.jpg"},{"name":"Intermediate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1577460/1baceaaf5ce81cd306b76b2fcf070ffab44da5b4.jpg"}],"total":20},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamst